snippet.title: Partymasters - Fun Idle Game
snippet.description:
Do u wanna be the new star of R’n’B? TAP-TAPOLICIOUS game starring the famous Lol Vein from Bowmasters.
 
Enjoy awesome dancers, cool money boosters, real hype, and all of your fans partying with you!

* 40+ awesome characters
* super-duper boosters to make THE SHOW

Dress up, follow the star way of Lol Vein, tap-tap, PARTY-UP!

Meet Lol Vein and his story of fame. See fun characters partyin’, make it money-rain, and get your party to the top!
